      <mj-column width="50%">
        <mj-text align="right">
          <p>June 2024</p>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section background-size="cover" background-url="https://info.locus.sh/hubfs/Emailer%20images/spotlight/jan2024/title-bg.jpg">
      <mj-column width="100%">
        <mj-text align="center" color="white" font-size="30px" padding="0 25px">
          <h1 class="fw-600">Locus in Spotlight</h1>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section background-color="white" padding="20px 25px" css-class="sec-pad">
      <mj-column width="100%">
        <mj-text>
          <p>Hi there!</p>
          <p>In this edition of our Locus in Spotlight newsletter, we talk about why cutting-edge logistics tech is not a choice but a <b>need</b> for retailers to stay competitive. Brands like Walmart agree with us.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text>
          <p>Have a great read!</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image padding-top="20px" src="https://info.locus.sh/hubfs/Emailer%20images/spotlight/jun2024/hero-image.webp" alt="hero image" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section background-color="white" padding="20px 25px" css-class="sec-pad">
      <mj-column width="100%">
        <mj-text font-size="30px" font-weight="800" line-height="1.2">
          <h2>Fuel for <span class="locus-blue">Thought</span></h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="10px" />
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column width="50%" vertical-align="middle">
        <mj-image align="left" css-class="mbl-img-left" src="https://info.locus.sh/hubfs/Emailer%20images/spotlight/jun2024/fuel-for-thought-image.webp" alt="fuel for thought image" />
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column width="50%" vertical-align="middle">
        <mj-text padding-left="0" css-class="mbl-pl-25">
          <a href="https://blog.locus.sh/strategies-to-compete-with-amazon-and-walmart-for-retailers/" class="locus-text td-none" target="_blank">Leveling the Retail Playing Field with Smart Tech: Compete with Walmart and Amazon</a><span class="locus-secondary-blue ft-rt">&nbsp;&#62;</span>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider padding-top="4px" padding-bottom="4px" padding-left="0" css-class="mbl-pl-25" border-width="0.5px" border-color="#290A38" />
        <mj-text padding-left="0" css-class="mbl-pl-25">
          <a href="https://locus.sh/reduce-wismo-calls-retail/" class="locus-text td-none" target="_blank">WISMO calls haunting your Customer Success team? We have the solution</a><span class="locus-secondary-blue ft-rt">&nbsp;&#62;</span>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider padding-top="4px" padding-bottom="4px" padding-left="0" css-class="mbl-pl-25" border-width="0.5px" border-color="#290A38" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section background-color="white" padding="10px 25px" css-class="sec-pad">
      <mj-column width="100%">
        <mj-text font-size="30px" font-weight="800" line-height="1.2">
          <h2>Build vs Buy: <span class="locus-orange">Walmart’s</span> Take!</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text>
          <p>Retail titans like Walmart have been known for building their own solutions inhouse. However, a few years back Walmart acknowledged partnering with a top supply chain software vendor for transforming their SCM operations.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text>
          <p>Why?</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text>
          <p>An off-the-shelf solution brings with it benefits like:</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text>
          <ul style="padding-left:1rem;">
            <li>Faster deployment time</li>
            <li>24/7 Support</li>
            <li>Highly Scalable</li>
            <li>Zero IT resource wastage</li>
          </ul>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text>
          <p>Locus is a smart order to delivery AI-powered solution that takes care of logistics operations for retail. Check out why brands like <b>Nestle, Unilever, Croma, Lulu Group</b> trust Locus with their retail fulfillment.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="5px" />
        <mj-button align="left" background-color="#3363FF" border-radius="0" font-weight="800" href="https://app.locus.sh/demo/retail.html?utm_source=newsletter&utm_medium=spotlight_june2024&utm_campaign=watch_demos">
          Watch Demo
        </mj-button>
        <mj-spacer height="5px" />
        <mj-text font-weight="600">
          <p>Still unsure? Here’s our definitive guide on why buying is better - <a class="locus-secondary-blue" href="https://locus.sh/whitepaper/buying-or-building-logistics-software/" target="_blank">Download Whitepaper</a></p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="15px" />
        <mj-divider border-color="#290A38" border-width="0.5px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section background-color="white" padding="20px 25px" css-class="sec-pad">
      <mj-column width="100%">
        <mj-text font-size="30px" font-weight="800" line-height="1.2">
          <h2>From our Social <span class="locus-purple">Feed</span></h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="5px" />
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column width="50%">
        <mj-image width="250px" padding-right="15px" css-class="mbl-img-left mbl-pr-25" src="https://info.locus.sh/hubfs/Emailer%20images/spotlight/jun2024/social-feed-image-1.webp" alt="social post image 1" />
        <mj-text padding-right="15px" css-class="mbl-pr-25">
          <p>A glimpse into our world at the Locus HQ in Bengaluru! Check out an exclusive sneak peek on LinkedIn, and explore exciting career opportunities with us.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-button align="left" background-color="#3363FF" border-radius="0" font-weight="800" href="https://www.linkedin.com/posts/locus-sh_office-lifeatlocus-locushq-activity-7203357951779049474-kq8O?utm_source=share&utm_medium=member_desktop">
          Check here
        </mj-button>
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column width="50%">
        <mj-image width="250px" padding-left="15px" css-class="mbl-img-left mbl-pl-25" src="https://info.locus.sh/hubfs/Emailer%20images/spotlight/jun2024/social-feed-image-2.webp" alt="social post image 2" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k0o78lp8KUg" />
        <mj-text padding-left="15px" css-class="mbl-pl-25">
          <p>We're turning 9! From a women’s safety app to a global logistics powerhouse, our journey has been nothing short of amazing. 1.2 billion deliveries, $303M+ saved, 82M miles reduced, and 14.4M kg CO2 cut!</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-button align="left" padding-left="15px" css-class="mbl-img-left mbl-pl-25" background-color="#3363FF" border-radius="0" font-weight="800" href="https://locus.sh/world-logistics-day/">
