        <mj-text font-size="30px" font-weight="800" line-height="1.2">
          <h2>A Word From Our <span class="locus-orange">Leaders</span></h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image padding-top="20px" padding-bottom="20px" src="https://info.locus.sh/hubfs/Emailer%20images/spotlight/jun2024/leaders-words-image.webp" alt="word from leaders image" />
        <mj-text font-weight="600">
          <p>Three Ways To Leverage Technology Solutions For Retail Returns Management</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text>
          <p class="fs-italic">“Choosing the right technology solutions for managing returns goes beyond the allure of advanced features like route optimization or real-time tracking. It's equally important to consider the level of support and flexibility offered. If you are working with a provider partner, consider their responsiveness to issues, their ability to scale with your business, and their programs' compatibility with your existing systems.”</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text font-weight="600">
          <p class="fs-italic">- Nishith Rastogi, CEO & Founder of Locus</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text font-weight="600">
          <a class="locus-secondary-blue" href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/forbesbusinesscouncil/2024/06/21/three-ways-to-leverage-technology-solutions-for-retail-returns-management/" target="_blank">Read more</a>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image align="left" width="100px" src="https://info.locus.sh/hubfs/Emailer%20images/spotlight/may2024/publisher-logo-2.webp" alt="publisher logo" />
        <mj-divider padding-top="20px" padding-bottom="20px" border-width="0.5px" border-color="#290A38" />
        <mj-text font-weight="600">
          <p>Towards greener future: Environmentally sustainable initiatives in the logistics sector</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text>
          <p class="fs-italic">“Today’s consumers are better informed and their purchases are value-driven. They favor brands that are not just about profits but also about purpose. By keeping a close track of and aligning with these ever-evolving expectations around sustainability, companies can cultivate loyalty and trust, transforming their brand into a banner for sustainability.”</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text font-weight="600">
          <p class="fs-italic">- Nishith Rastogi, CEO & Founder of Locus</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text font-weight="600">
          <a class="locus-secondary-blue" href="https://www.financialexpress.com/sustainability-2/towards-greener-future-environmentally-sustainable-initiatives-in-the-logistics-sector/3514854/" target="_blank">Read more</a>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image align="left" width="175px" src="https://info.locus.sh/hubfs/Emailer%20images/spotlight/jun2024/logo-financial-express.webp" alt="publisher logo" />
        <mj-divider padding-top="20px" padding-bottom="20px" border-width="0.5px" border-color="#290A38" />
        <mj-text font-weight="600">
          <p>Driving Innovation and Sustainability in Logistics</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text>
          <p class="fs-italic">“Engaging with local stakeholders is key to our success. We hold regular discussions with local partners, customers, and industry experts to gain insights into cultural nuances and business practices. This cultural understanding helps us build trust and credibility in each market.”</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text font-weight="600">
          <p class="fs-italic">- Mehul Kapadia, Chief Revenue Officer, Locus</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text font-weight="600">
          <a class="locus-secondary-blue" href="https://www.prittleprattlenews.com/technology/locussh/" target="_blank">Read more</a>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image align="left" width="175px" src="https://info.locus.sh/hubfs/Emailer%20images/spotlight/jun2024/logo-pp-news.webp" alt="publisher logo" />
        <mj-spacer height="20px" />
